00:02:40.640 --> 00:02:41.680
I've wronged you.

00:02:46.400 --> 00:02:48.040
Take my head to His Majesty,

00:02:50.560 --> 00:02:52.240
and he won't punish the Xiao family.

00:02:53.680 --> 00:02:54.680
I only ask...

00:02:56.080 --> 00:02:57.280
